---
title: Turkey Pasta E Fagioli Soup with Garlicky Breadsticks & Parsley
description: This soul-warming vegan soup is the culinary equivalent of a cozy blanket. It’s chock full of goodness, with earthy cannellini and kidney beans, tender onion and celery, and springy couscous in a savory tomato and mushroom broth. Throw in lots of fresh parsley, serve with a side of crisp garlic breadsticks, and you’ve got an ideal vegan dinner or lunch idea! Get ready to wrap yourself in this meal that’s as satisfying and comforting as it is delicious.
